{"type": "article", "id": 16934, "title": "这个迷人的窗户设计，想让你多看到一点天空", "description": "尽管我们这儿的天不总是蓝的吧，但窗户有趣一点不是啥坏事啊。", "date": "2015-11-02T13:33:32Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 435, "name": "室内设计"}, {"id": 18124, "name": "Aldana Ferrer Garcia"}], "category": 17, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 19, "praise_count": 261, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160606150802KSroaqBm2yT1sItC.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自阿根廷的建筑师 Aldana Ferrer Garcia 设计了这些折叠打开的窗户，一共三种，他为它们取了一个有幻想意义的名字“more sky”。 \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t“hopper niche”是最大众的一种，只有一个 15° 的倾斜，看上去像是将常年打开的窗户用玻璃固定起来，可以无顾忌地趴在上面。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150757PfyAJ7ZhQKDkRC6N.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.81418093\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150757QRyf4HgxvbWVn8E2.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"1.12958435\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150758F1E6vhGdCBr43IHA.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.82273839\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/2016060615075840QmCPcYbWzOpvIU.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8594132\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t“awning niche”，看起来像将 3 个“hopper niche”反向叠加起来，与垂直墙面构成 45°，正好是一个做躺椅的空间，可以舒服地仰望天空。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150759cF1YSmIHrbtaMkEv.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80440098\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150759tn6Kvcdf1ZqOeXIF.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.87652812\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150759gMqPzZ0pFYd8uxUE.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.68826406\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t\"casement niche\"像是将平开窗的空间用玻璃封闭起来，构成一个圆弧，可以直接坐在里面看书或者沉思，悬在半空时说不定能促进思考。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150800lP96bzosJUkycAjL.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.80806846\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150800aCWbzZAIdRmg2UoB.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.8398533\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t这组设计正在迪拜设计周上展示，它可以适应不同窗户的实际大小。<a href=\"http://aldanaferrergarcia.com/#/moresky/\" target=\"_blank\">这里是设计师的工作室。</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150800vz8G3KqlcXgj7rQT.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.76405868\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150801zjt9DhOGYd41lyIf.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.74816626\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span> </span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150801r3ag10X4DQZzkuKO.jpg\" title=\" \" alt=\" \" data-ratio=\"0.95354523\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\r\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606150802tecwzn79kEbN5D0o.jpg\" title=\"手稿图\" alt=\"手稿图\" data-ratio=\"0.7707151\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><span>手稿图</span> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t图片来自 <a href=\"http://www.designboom.com/design/dubai-design-week-global-grad-showaldana-ferrer-garcia-more-sky-10-31-2015/\" target=\"_blank\">designboom</a> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n</p>\n\n\n"}